{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/hr.png?t=1728553431\" /><br><strong>CINEMA</strong> is an immersive <strong>thriller</strong> adventure game where the player wields <strong>control over time</strong> and the intricate interplay of cause and effect within an environment inspired by <strong>silent films</strong>. With the ability to navigate diverse <strong>timelines</strong> and even create entirely new ones, the player experiences a unique and captivating gameplay mechanic.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/title_noirAdventure.png?t=1728553431\" /><br>Interact with mysterious characters while gathering crucial clues and evidence to solve the case.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/Cinema_Wide_0.gif?t=1728553431\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/title_timeManipulation.png?t=1728553431\" /><br>Navigate through time by moving both forward and backward, and explore rich Art Deco environments across space and moments in time.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/Cinema_Wide_1.gif?t=1728553431\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/title_timeLines.png?t=1728553431\" /><br>Use information from the future to change events in the past, creating new timelines to solve complex crimes and uncover hidden truths.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/Cinema_Wide_2.gif?t=1728553431\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144070/extras/hr_small.png?t=17